# 🎨 Styling Rules

## Tailwind & Tokens

- Prefer Tailwind utility classes; avoid inline styles.
- Use CSS variables for theme colors: `--primary`, `--workout`, `--idle` (+ `-soft`, `-glow`).
- Dark mode via `dark:` class; keep variables in `index.css`.
- Use `cn()` for conditional class composition.

## Layout & Components

- Mobile-first responsive (`sm`, `md`, `lg`).
- Reusable visuals: `glass-card`, `timer-display`, `progress-ring-*`.
- Animations from `tailwind.config.ts`: `animate-fade-in`, `animate-slide-up`, `animate-scale-in`; set delays with inline style when needed.
- Keep component variants explicit (`variant="focus" | "workout"`, `size` props).

## Do / Don’t

- ✅ Use Tailwind + CSS vars for all colors/shadows.
- ✅ Keep styles colocated with components via classNames.
- ❌ No CSS-in-JS; ❌ no hardcoded hex colors; ❌ no global CSS outside `@layer`.
